 class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無罪就快D走<br />\n到上訴就遲"},{"pid":"99eea5a2c90e8a1565aa3bf725084db0a0a43886","tid":2430973,"uid":52271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:47:56.000Z","msg":"快走"},{"pid":"4a48320a2d75127b72f815db73011122b5f20eb4","tid":2430973,"uid":158404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:48:37.000Z","msg":"鐵筆都唔撚得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b47a533658d5c6fdb769d96c372c1dfc70bcf0a","tid":2430973,"uid":282359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T10:51:01.000Z","msg":"啲判決彈弓手到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一個人嘅前途竟然要完全靠撞手神。真係好撚癲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"748026eac2a9fb4eeb5ccebf03901f238263a519","tid":2430973,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ad21be590b1ecd6f80514e1480e38cbdf532b6e","tid":2430973,"uid":53498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:16:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fccdbcf72fe3f22b12a2dd8b0d808ae5adb9e1e4","tid":2430973,"uid":56115,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-03T11:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}